				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">SM2 is not ONLY good when pet canni was around.
<br />

<br />
go to droga.  make a pet, fully buffed, sm2 it, invis, run to where you want to kill a mob, bring out pet, kill mob, sm2 it, invis, run to the next target, etc etc etc.
<br />

<br />
sm2 is also very useful on raids if you need to invis or need to get rid of your pet, but dont want to waste time summoning a new one.
<br />

<br />
Pet canni was just ONE of the MANY things SM2 was useful for, saying that its "worthless" or "useless" now is just plain dumb.
<br />

<br />
its invaluable in droga and nurga for mad farming, and many other zones.<br />_________________<br />Anitalynn WindRyder
<br />
65 Arch Convoker (51 AA)
<br />
Rodcet Nife</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
